### ðŸ§¬ Core Idea
PTC (Proof of Time Contribution) is a decentralized, blockchain-based eldercare token model. Rather than relying on state-issued pensions, individuals accumulate spiritual â€œcreditâ€ through their vibrational presence in the **Mother Theater**.

Through AI-guided scripts, frequency logs, and meaningful participation, elder souls mint PTC tokens, which younger souls can purchase as claims for future care. PTC can then be exchanged for local fiat currencies.

### ðŸ§± System Architecture
