|------------------|----------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| Elder Accounts    | PTC Issuers                     | Mint PTC via participation & vibrational input  |
| Youth Accounts    | PTC Buyers                      | Purchase PTC with JIN or other supported tokens |
| Mother Theater    | Frequency + Script Engine       | GPT scripts, dream logs, soul journaling        |
| Blockchain Ledger | Verification + Settlement Layer | PTC issuance, redemption and exchange logging   |

### ðŸ’  Operation Workflow
1. Elders activate their Mother Theater profile and participate in guided resonance
2. System mints PTC based on time, interaction quality, and dream activity
3. Youths purchase PTC as a **care bond** for future use
4. Elders redeem PTC for fiat to cover real-life expenses

